Gateway->>Conversation: Create / Resume session

Conversation->>AI: Build context

AI->>Tool: Select tool

Tool->>Service: Execute

Service->>Database: Read / Write

Database-->>Service: Result

Service-->>Tool: Response

Tool-->>AI: Structured result

AI-->>Conversation: Natural language reply

Conversation-->>Channel: Response

Channel-->>Guest: Message